{"tid":1359663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中俄轟炸機入侵南韓防空識別區 南韓開火警告 俄羅斯斥南韓不專業","createTime":"2019-07-24T07:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:27:33.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bf2b0f01f05bc3da0b8a02349f8a7164f7b07f11","tid":1359663,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:41:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2487922204604265&amp;id=420361564693683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2487922204604265%26id%3D420361564693683&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=b8f8aa60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2487922204604265&amp;id=420361564693683</a><br />\n<br />\n【中俄軍機闖南韓防空識別區 南韓開火示警俄反斥不專業】<br />\n<br />\n中國與俄羅斯軍機周二（7月23日）首次同時闖入南韓防空識別區。南韓戰機開火示警，俄方事後否認侵犯南韓領空，批評南韓戰機舉動不專業；北京則指會向軍方了解。<br />\n<br />\n南韓指，周二早上共有五架軍機，闖入南韓防空識別區，包括中國軍方兩架轟6轟炸機，及俄羅斯兩架圖95轟炸機，其中轟6轟炸機更是三度闖入。<br />\n<br />\n同日上午，俄方一架A-50預警機也兩次闖入南韓與日本有主權爭議、南韓稱為獨島的上空，南韓派戰機兩次開火示警。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-24-2019/54574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-24-2019%2F54574&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=002a1ff5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-24-2019/54574</a><br />\n#南韓 #防空識別區 #中國 #俄羅斯<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=f6175669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=d4dce760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise2&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=6def1a27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血主持育成計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=11d789da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise</a><br />\n<br />\n《熱血時報》 iOS，Android 同步抗共，歡迎下載：<br />\n<br />\niPhone<br />\n<a href=\"https://apple.co/2IfgPoP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2IfgPoP&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=2862307b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2IfgPoP</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HqB4Q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HqB4Q4&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=64e8882d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HqB4Q4</a><br />\n--------------------<br />\n成功之前，我們絕對不要放棄夢想！<br />\nTill our dreams come true, we'll fight on."},{"pid":"1ead949e8661832d518a1452551b4a6c29618108","tid":1359663,"uid":70760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:43:00.000Z","msg":"又要威又要帶頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a84b74a7629d9e3bcecf59f2796d800d826f67","tid":1359663,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:43:41.000Z","msg":"理鳩你專唔專業，work就得啦"},{"pid":"3803b324af86cf7ac2b5ccbad682a8d9dec8f9bf","tid":1359663,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/